            </tuv>
            <tuv xml:lang="en">
                <seg>it was adorned with hundreds of thousands of pinnacles made of solid gold, was furnished with round mirrors made of the essence of a thousand precious materials, and was adorned with countless precious jewels;</seg>
            </tuv>
