            </tuv>
            <tuv xml:lang="en">
                <seg>Sudhana, the head merchant’s son, approached the bhikṣu Sudarśana and bowed his head onto the surface of the bhikṣu Sudarśana’s feet, covered the surface of the bhikṣu Sudarśana’s feet with kisses, and wiped them well.</seg>
            </tuv>
        </tu>
