                <seg>“In one instant of mind, through the power of accomplishing the bodhisattva’s completely good conduct and prayers, I directly perceive an anabhilāpyānabhilāpya­parivarta of gateways of the ways of conduct among beings in order to complete the wisdoms of the ten strengths.</seg>
            </tuv>
