            <tuv xml:lang="bo">
                <seg>བྱང་ཆུབ་སེམས་དཔའ་ཐམས་ཅད་ཀྱི་སྨོན་ལམ་ཆེན་པོ་ལ་ལྟ་བ།</seg>
            </tuv>
            <tuv xml:lang="en">
                <seg>he was focused on the great prayers of all bodhisattvas so as to maintain bodhisattva conduct throughout all kalpas;</seg>
            </tuv>
        </tu>
        <tu id="UT22084-037-007-TU-3056">
            <prop name="location-id">UT22084-037-007-2283</prop>
