            </tuv>
            <tuv xml:lang="en">
                <seg>Veṣṭhila replied, “Noble one, when I am resting in this samādhi,  there appear to me all the tathāgatas, such as Kāśyapa, in a continuous succession of one buddha after another within the lineage of this world:</seg>
            </tuv>
