            </tuv>
            <tuv xml:lang="en">
                <seg>“Noble one, in that way, I created roots of merit under one buddha after another, and for as many kalpas as there are atoms in Sumeru , I traveled on easy and level paths without any impediment, but I had not yet accomplished the powers of a bodhisattva.</seg>
            </tuv>
